<h2 id="Syntax">Syntax</h2>
<pre class="twopartsyntaxbox"><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax" title="CSS/Value_definition_syntax">Formal syntax</a>: <code>none <a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#Single_bar" title="Single bar: the two entities are optional, but exactly one must be present.">|</a> <a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/image" title="">&lt;image&gt;</a></code> 
</pre>
<pre>border-image-source: none                                  /* no border-image, use the specified border-style */
border-image-source: url(image.jpg)                        /* the image.jpg is used as image */
border-image-source: linear-gradient(to top, red, yellow)  /* a gradient is used as image */

border-image-source: inherit
</pre>